{"tid":2150260,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"嘆法國治安差 黃祥興遭刀手搶車","createTime":"2020-08-11T00:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T07:23:32.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e686d0982e58000b492ba7192a6b52a9cbfac198","tid":2150260,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T00:53:06.000Z","msg":"藝人黃祥興與黃婉曼昨午現身電視城，出席myTV SUPER全新節目《搬家》記者會。該節目探討移民資訊，曾在法國生活20年的祥興說：「其實當地治安差少少，我記得10歲左右，試過畀人出刀仔明搶單車，之後我就開始練大隻，唔打得都嚇得吖嘛！」由於擔心家人安全，他選擇舉家回流返港，問會否考慮移民其他地方，他說：「或者會送小朋友去加拿大讀書，但要讀完小學先，我想佢哋打好中文同廣東話嘅根基。」<br />\n<br />\n至於黃婉曼則透露近日忙搬家：「小朋友畀疫情困咗大半年，搬去新界啲嘅地方，人少啲環境好啲，等佢哋有空間走動。我仲犧牲咗自己個衣帽間，改建成Playroom，等佢哋玩得開心啲！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rj146rIcgra9N1MF51YWwQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/fa170b4ae2871474ebccc43e91a699cf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Frj146rIcgra9N1MF51YWwQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Ffa170b4ae2871474ebccc43e91a699cf&h=85d8b63f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5946222525c2e727a4f6f3a4509dcb4bd04a805","tid":2150260,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T00:57:37.000Z","msg":"粘冰冰對波好似縮咗水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc760e2cbd138985c239e224cfb650d9395eb278","tid":2150260,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T01:01:27.000Z","msg":"黃唔係嫁咗有米人仕，重要出來做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd66bee512d4a37dc0202645d09b1d54217fa73","tid":2150260,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T01:03:13.000Z","msg":"出到外國要表明自己係香港人，唔係中國人，OK?"},{"pid":"fbf3dd712a25e5eab9c7a5c3f61d56513535d2d6","tid":2150260,"uid":54486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r